del is used\nto evaluate the bed load transport rate, which is in satisfactory agreement\nwith common formulae based on flume data, especially when compared against\nother saltation-derived expressions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2016 23:26:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-14"}
